---
title: Italian Chicken Sausage & Cavatappi Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinner? A DIY pasta bar! You’ll set out springy cavatappi pasta, roasted zucchini, savory chicken sausage, two sauces—marinara and lemon-garlic cream—crunchy toasted panko, and Parmesan cheese family style so everyone can create their perfect pasta plate. Order extra broccoli for more veggies, or add chicken cutlets!

